video.title: Falsa identidad
video.synopsis: Strangers Diego and Isabel flee their home in Mexico and pretend to be a married couple to escape his drug-dealing enemies and her abusive husband.

episodes.synopsis: The mayor hatches a plan to hide his brother from Gavino's cartel and Isabel from her abusive husband. Gavino puts a price on Diego's head.
episodes.title: Isabel and Diego's challenge

episodes.synopsis: Isabel, Diego, and little Ricardo cross into the United States. They are now Camila, Emiliano, and Max Guevara. Eliseo declares war on Gavino.
episodes.title: Isabel and Diego flee to the United States

episodes.synopsis: Eliseo learns that Augusto, the Sonora boss, financed his campaign. To prove it, he gives Circe the coordinates for the next shipment of cocaine.
episodes.title: Circe betrays her father

episodes.synopsis: After losing the goods to the feds, Gavino discovers who sold him out. Isabel, Ricardo, and Diego arrive in Mexico City. Isabel's daughter disappears.
episodes.title: Gavino threatens Circe

episodes.synopsis: Thrown out of her house, Circe moves in with Joselito, who says he's the reason she's still alive. Augusto fakes a kidnapping. Isabel can't find work.
episodes.title: Circe and Joselito make love

episodes.synopsis: Amanda is in danger every second she's with her father. Isabel begins working at a cabaret to be able to pay a good lawyer, and Diego wants to help.
episodes.title: Isabel will do anything for her daughter

episodes.synopsis: Gavino's daughter seeks revenge on Diego, so she seduces Joselito and promises to please him in return for a favor. Piochas and Deivid find Isabel.
episodes.title: Circe requests Eliseo's head

episodes.synopsis: Emiliano Guevara is interviewed after saving a man's life. Eliseo is annoyed with his brother and resigns from his job to run for governor.
episodes.title: Diego is exposed on television

episodes.synopsis: Isabel lies to Diego about her job again and he plans to expose her. Joselito's thug corners Eliseo. Camila confronts Ramona.
episodes.title: Isabel has a secret

episodes.synopsis: Diego is jealous when Isabel dances for others and demands she quit. Eliseo knows Joselito was with his attacker. Marlene sees Lourdes being taken.
episodes.title: Isabel and Diego kiss

episodes.synopsis: Zoraida gives Eliseo the gun her stepfather used to kill the prosecutor in return for help saving Amanda. Joselito won't give in to Circe's blackmail.
episodes.title: Eliseo suspects Augusto

episodes.synopsis: Isabel tells Diego she's in love with him; they spend the night together. Eliseo faces Augusto. Gavino learns Diego is back; he orders a manhunt.
episodes.title: Isabel and Diego make love

episodes.synopsis: Amanda's rescue gets tricky. Corona appears to stop Isabel from taking her daughter. Diego confronts him; the three escape. Gavino gets bad news.
episodes.title: Amanda's rescue

episodes.synopsis: Circe leaves Joselito at the altar and threatens Eliseo so he will take her to Diego. Isabel won't leave Diego. Corona files a kidnapping report.
episodes.title: Circe leaves everything for Diego

episodes.synopsis: Circe frames Gavino. The feds arrest the Boss. Diego appears at his brother's house and thinks he's kidnapped.
episodes.title: Circe kills Diego's brother

episodes.synopsis: Diego confirms who killed Eliseo and swears revenge. Isabel looks for Diego at the funeral. Joselito orders Circe's murder.
episodes.title: Diego is at a loss for his brother

episodes.synopsis: Gavino's men come to the funeral to kill Circe and Diego. Isabel is in love. Joselito finds Circe and ties her up. Gavino is beaten in prison.
episodes.title: An attack is made on Eliseo's wake

episodes.synopsis: Diego tells Isabel he loves her and wants to start a family. Corona finds out who killed his mother. Joselito orders Deivid's mother killed.
episodes.title: Isabel and Diego settle down

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda is suicidal because of what has happened to her. Joselito wants to make Circe ask for forgiveness. Gavino is eager to get out of prison.
episodes.title: Fernanda is put in the street

episodes.synopsis: After the cartel puts a price on their heads, Circe and Felipa go to Mexico City. Corona drops the charges. Diego wants to go to Babel with Isabel.
episodes.title: Circe arrives at Babel

episodes.synopsis: The cartel doesn't have a bead on Circe or Diego and thinks they left together. Joselito orders Fernanda to be kidnapped. Jim makes Isabel an offer.
episodes.title: Joselito orders a kidnapping

episodes.synopsis: Gavino is badly hurt in a prison attack. Joselito wants him dead so he can lead the cartel. Fernanda arrives at Diego's house. Jim seeks investors.
episodes.title: Gavino on the brink of death

episodes.synopsis: With Augusto's money and Brandon's aid, Circe will wipe out the Gaonas to form the world's strongest cartel. Isabel learns who Marlene's boyfriend is.
episodes.title: Circe creates her own cartel

episodes.synopsis: Circe seizes the Gaonas' business. Corona finds his son. Piochas plans to rescue Gavino. Isabel learns what Augusto is doing.
episodes.title: Circe's great moment

episodes.synopsis: Isabel tells Diego that Porfirio is closing in. Diego will do anything to protect his family. The Colombians make other deals, but Joselito finds out.
episodes.title: Diego gets up the nerve

episodes.synopsis: Circe learns Diego is with another woman and swears to have no mercy. Corona comes to Isabel's house. Piochas looks to get Gavino out of the hospital.
episodes.title: Diego rejects Circe

episodes.synopsis: The new dancer at Babel catches Circe's eye; she asks to meet her, not knowing she's with Diego. Corona reveals Diego and Fernanda's location.
episodes.title: Circe meets Camila

episodes.synopsis: Diego decides to go because the cartel may return for him. Joselito gets Isabel's photo. Circe successfully moves drugs. Gavino knows he was betrayed.
episodes.title: Joselito lets Diego live

episodes.synopsis: Joselito confirms Camila is with Diego and has her take him to the table. Corona and Diego fight over Isabel. Circe agrees to meet the Gaonas.
episodes.title: Joselito recognizes Isabel

episodes.synopsis: Joselito continues toying with Camila. She thinks it's under control and he doesn't recognize her. Augusto realizes who killed Eliseo.
episodes.title: Camila flirts with Joselito

episodes.synopsis: Joselito meets Hot Mama and learns that she is Circe. They threaten each other's lives over the drug trade. The dancers are at risk.
episodes.title: Circe and Joselito face to face

episodes.synopsis: Joselito goes crazy when he finds out that the waitresses escaped. Diego learns the truth about Babel. The warden orders Gavino back to his cell.
episodes.title: Danger finds Isabel in Babel

episodes.synopsis: Isabel asks for Diego's forgiveness. Upset, he asks for space to decide if they should stay together. Circe visits Gavino in prison; he attacks her.
episodes.title: Diego distances himself from Isabel

episodes.synopsis: Hot Mama has one day to move the goods and wants Diego as a guide. Joselito can give her the location. Diego contacts the real Emiliano's aunt.
episodes.title: Circe wants to recruit Diego

episodes.synopsis: With the information Joselito gives her, Circe figures out who robbed her man. Joselito visits Gavino in prison. Corona's condition worsens.
episodes.title: Circe arrives at Diego's house

episodes.synopsis: After Circe's visit, Diego tells Isabel the truth about his past. They promise to start over. Marlene begins to suspect Augusto.
episodes.title: Isabel and Diego reconcile

episodes.synopsis: The Colombians want to see their goods arrive. If Circe can't hold up her end, they'll get back at her and Diego. The Gaonas have Brandon and Augusto.
episodes.title: Circe receives a threat

episodes.synopsis: Joselito intercepts the truckload of drugs. Fernanda finds out who her husband's lover is. Isabel wants to help her children's father.
episodes.title: The plot set against Joselito

episodes.synopsis: Joselito seeks revenge on Diego. Hot Mama seduces Diego. Corona goes to the hospital. Joselito interrogates Augusto and orders Felipa kidnapped.
episodes.title: Joselito sends a message

episodes.synopsis: The Gaonas have Felipa. Circe and the girls arrive at Babel to rescue her. Diego accepts the Colombians' offer. Fernanda confronts Augusto.
episodes.title: Circe receives a big hit

episodes.synopsis: To protect her kids, Isabel decides to leave her fake marriage. Circe has half the country after Joselito: she offers a million dollars for his head.
episodes.title: Isabel quits the farce

episodes.synopsis: Circe learns that Diego is a free man and seeks to win back the love of her life. Gavino starts doing business in jail. Deivid advises Chucho.
episodes.title: Luck is on Circe's side

episodes.synopsis: Joselito can't stand Diego working with Circe and sends his men out to get him. Corona wants to get back his family and his wife's love.
episodes.title: Isabel's children are taken

episodes.synopsis: Piochas and Mateo prepare an ambush to get rid of Joselito and obtain the reward. Isabel doesn't want to see Diego again. Circe casts a love spell.
episodes.title: The plan to kill Joselito

episodes.synopsis: Corona's health deteriorates. Isabel is ready to do anything to save her children's father. Diego and Circe take territory from Joselito.
episodes.title: Corona, closer to death

episodes.synopsis: The Gaonas attack Hot Mama's warehouse, and Joselito does everything he can to get her. Circe tries to escape but is shot. Fernanda divorces Augusto.
episodes.title: Joselito goes after Circe

episodes.synopsis: Diego rescues Circe and takes her to his house to heal her wounds. Hot Mama reminds him that he's hers. Isabel decides to give herself a chance.
episodes.title: The passion of Diego

episodes.synopsis: After the real Emiliano's aunt visits, Isabel looks for Diego. When she finds him, she gets the surprise of her life. Circe frames Augusto.
episodes.title: Isabel with the broken heart

episodes.synopsis: Hot Mama wants to multitask: if Joselito and Augusto will come to her, she can kill them both. Marlene can't believe her fiance is a killer.
episodes.title: Circe makes a move

episodes.synopsis: Circe enjoys seeing Joselito and Augusto tied up and decides to take what's owed her. Mateo wants to start a new business. Marlene confronts Diego.
episodes.title: Circe's sweet revenge

episodes.synopsis: Isabel's need is growing. She is looking for work and tells Paloma one of her biggest secrets. Diego feels betrayed by his loved ones.
episodes.title: Paloma confronts Camila

episodes.synopsis: Desperate to see his stepfather, Diego gets Circe to take him to where Joselito and Augusto are; something unexpected happens. Gavino has a plan.
episodes.title: Circe and Diego are in for a surprise

episodes.synopsis: Joselito has to change plans and find help to regain power. Circe, Diego, and the Colombians know where he is and corner him.
episodes.title: Joselito's other face

episodes.synopsis: Diego goes to the hospital to get rid of Augusto. Circe wants to kill the man she loves before he learns the truth. Marlene makes a wedding decision.
episodes.title: Diego sleeps with the enemy

episodes.synopsis: Things get even worse for Isabel; Margot Guevara threatens to put her in prison. Circe has a hard time seeing Diego at his brother's grave.
episodes.title: Isabel exposed

episodes.synopsis: Circe must decide if she wants to do the same as Diego. He wants to make a change in his life. Isabel looks for Diego. Margot wants more evidence.
episodes.title: Diego's new plan

episodes.synopsis: Isabel can't leave the city. Diego wants to talk to Margot to tell her the truth. Augusto agrees to testify on Gavino's behalf.
episodes.title: Diego ready to face the music

episodes.synopsis: Margot is about to find proof of Isabel and Diego's charade. Circe makes them look for Emiliano's aunt. Isabel gets an opportunity to flee.
episodes.title: A ticking time bomb for Isabel and Diego

episodes.synopsis: To separate Diego and Isabel, Circe finds Emiliano's aunt to threaten her, but she loses control. Marlene confronts Augusto; Mateo blackmails Isabel.
episodes.title: Circe stains her hands with blood for Diego

episodes.synopsis: Diego knows that Circe is involved with the Guevaras' aunt's death. She learns Margot thwarted her plans to leave with him. Isabel wants the truth.
episodes.title: Circe exposes herself

episodes.synopsis: Augusto attests to Gavino's innocence and says Joselito is the real cartel boss. Isabel feels like she's to blame. Circe and Diego plan to leave.
episodes.title: Augusto publicly accuses Joselito

episodes.synopsis: Hot Mama's dream of leaving with Diego is interrupted when they get an ultimatum they must comply with. Diana and Gaby get into trouble.
episodes.title: Circe and Diego must pay a high price

episodes.synopsis: Hot Mama visits her father in prison. She confronts him and the Boss fires back, telling her Felipa's deepest secret. Gaby may be deported.
episodes.title: Circe's world collapses

episodes.synopsis: Circe is furious with Felipa and wants to kill her. Diego shares his plan with Deivid. Corona and Mateo get out of surgery. Augusto attacks Marlene.
episodes.title: Hot Mama punishes Felipa

episodes.synopsis: Hot Mama plans to get out of the business, but Gavino is ready to bring her down. She doesn't know what she's up against. Diego plans his last move.
episodes.title: Gavino prepares a surprise

episodes.synopsis: At Gavino's trial, Augusto testifies on his behalf; Eliseo's memory becomes tainted. Isabel learns that Diego and Circe are leaving the country.
episodes.title: All in Gavino Gaona's favor

episodes.synopsis: The Boss makes his move and achieves his goals. He begins to take revenge by killing all his enemies and capturing Circe. Diego looks for Gavino.
episodes.title: Gavino's great victory

episodes.synopsis: Circe begins to feel her father's wrath. The Boss does his best to leave her without allies or a way out; he talks to Ramona to learn her escape plan.
episodes.title: Gavino is more dangerous than ever before

episodes.synopsis: The Boss and Diego are even. Each one has in his power someone important to the other and is sure that the other will do everything to find her.
episodes.title: Gavino's heavy hit

episodes.synopsis: After getting some of his enemies together, Gavino proposes a truce to Diego. Circe tries to save her business. Joselito decides to return to Mexico.
episodes.title: Diego is speechless

episodes.synopsis: Desperate, Hot Mama thinks Diego can save her, not knowing that he's waiting for the moment to attack. Marlene talks about her feelings for Jim.
episodes.title: Circe's right-hand man

episodes.synopsis: Gavino sows discord between Circe and Diego. Augusto tries to take advantage of Marlene's sister. Gaby wants to go to the U.S., far from Deivid.
episodes.title: Circe and Diego look each other in the eye

episodes.synopsis: After buttering up Circe, Diego makes an offer. She says they will get the goods back soon. The Colombians are uneasy about Joselito's return.
episodes.title: Diego's proposal

episodes.synopsis: Thinking she knows what Diego is up to, Circe calls him, but he decides not to talk to her. Porfirio learns that the feds are looking for his father.
episodes.title: Hot Mama's new surprise

episodes.synopsis: Isabel goes to Alamos with Diego, but is followed by security cameras there. Circe confronts her father.
episodes.title: Isabel ready to die

episodes.synopsis: Gavino swears Circe is out of the business; he visits the Colombians to get more power, but all is not as it seems. Isabel and Diego work as a team.
episodes.title: The Gaona cartel's deal

episodes.synopsis: Although Diego wants to keep Isabel out of his plans, she won't leave his side. Gavino wants Circe out of the drug trade. Joselito is about to attack.
episodes.title: The passion of Isabel and Diego

episodes.synopsis: Joselito plans to take out Gavino at Babel. When he's about to kill the Boss, something happens to change his plans. Porfirio and Paloma are together.
episodes.title: Joselito attacks Gavino

episodes.synopsis: Circe still thinks she has control of Diego, but she misses something. The feds get Joselito; Gavino wants his head. Mateo wants to show his loyalty.
episodes.title: Diego in Circe's claws

episodes.synopsis: As the feds are moving Joselito, they are caught in an ambush. Mateo shows he is loyal to Gavino. Diego is close to his goal, but Circe is suspicious.
episodes.title: Joselito's days are numbered

episodes.synopsis: Gavino wants to settle scores with Joselito. Nuria endures a traumatic episode. Circe begins to investigate Diego. Jim sets fire to Babel.
episodes.title: Joselito lives in hell

episodes.synopsis: Gavino finds Circe and leaves her a chilling message. Diego asks for immunity for Isabel and himself. Porfirio threatens to take Isabel's children.
episodes.title: Circe receives a grim present

episodes.synopsis: Diego plans to capture Circe, who faces her worst nightmare. Agent Williams finds Isabel's house. Gavino wants to ally with Alex Mendez.
episodes.title: Diego exposed

episodes.synopsis: Diego wants to avenge his brother's death, but Hot Mama has a different plan. Williams has the proof he needs to arrest Isabel and Diego.
episodes.title: Circe's sinister plan

episodes.synopsis: After an attempt at capture fails, Diego and Circe come clean. Gavino's ruse is exposed. Isabel agrees to be separated from her children.
episodes.title: Diego declares war on Circe

episodes.synopsis: There's only one way for Diego to protect Isabel and the children. Fernanda's restaurant is attacked. Circe has a new ally. Amanda disappears.
episodes.title: Diego's difficult decision

episodes.synopsis: After Gavino's attack, Diego decides to take justice into his own hands. Mateo goes behind Gavino's back. Isabel threatens her father-in-law.
episodes.title: Diego in the wolf's mouth

episodes.synopsis: Isabel's worst nightmare becomes reality and there's no way out. Marlene finds Jim. Circe accepts Mateo's offer. Nuria confesses to her addiction.
episodes.title: Isabel and her children are taken

episodes.synopsis: The leader of the Gaonas falls into Mateo's trap. Circe seeks revenge. Isabel and Diego receive an offer. Salas turns himself in to the authorities.
episodes.title: Circe corners Gavino

episodes.synopsis: The war between father and daughter ends. Isabel is on the verge of death; Diego and Porfirio work together to save her. Salas says he's to blame.
episodes.title: The Gaonas final duel

episodes.synopsis: Isabel and Diego are ready to be a family, but an enemy is lurking. Circe tries to escape. Paloma loses a loved one. Fernanda says goodbye to Salas.
episodes.title: Isabel and Diego's new life

episodes.synopsis: Diego and Isabel are in a witness protection program, but he breaks the rules to get in touch with his mother Fernanda. Ignacio Salas remains free.
episodes.title: Huir del presente

episodes.synopsis: Circe faces murder, drug trafficking and money laundering charges. Rogelio receives a cry for help. The Sonora prosecutor intervenes, with conditions.
episodes.title: La caída de Circe

episodes.synopsis: Amanda goes to meet her grandfather. Isabel's love for her daughter is so great that it pushes her to make a drastic decision to get her family back.
episodes.title: Todo queda atrás

episodes.synopsis: The die is cast. Now that hatred is Circe's driving force, heads will roll. Mami Chula and El Buitre join forces for revenge.
episodes.title: Un trato macabro

episodes.synopsis: Badly wounded, Diego takes refuge in a church to flee Mateo's men, who are armed to the teeth. Victoria and Father Rafael must make a decision.
episodes.title: Refugio eclesiástico

episodes.synopsis: Diego and Isabel are so close, yet so far. Victoria and Father Rafael begin the escape plan, but El Pollo is suspicious. Fernanda confronts Mateo.
episodes.title: Coincidencia incalculable

episodes.synopsis: Amanda tells her grandfather how she and her brother suffered at the hands of Circe and Alex. Ramona must pick a side: her lover's or her niece's?
episodes.title: Lealtad a prueba

episodes.synopsis: Circe and El Buitre are together and everyone is talking. Mateo goes to look for them. A tense situation may cost the Arismendi family dearly.
episodes.title: Revuelo en La Esperanza

episodes.synopsis: Diego, Deivid and Chucho follow Circe's trail to the cemetery. Mami Chula thinks she sees Joselito among the tombstones. Diana goes to the police.
episodes.title: Reencuentro con los muertos

episodes.synopsis: Rosa just wants to flee, but Circe insists on going after Diego to finish him. Diana ends up in the hospital. Chucho suffers a painful interrogation.
episodes.title: Oportunidad de oro

episodes.synopsis: Isabel takes a risk, says goodbye to Ricas, and meets The Man. She puts her plan into action once at the hotel... not thinking of the consequences.
episodes.title: Los encantos de Isabel

episodes.synopsis: Mateo finds Circe's hideout and goes after her. El Buitre and his father become unwilling accomplices. Mami Chula hears when Claudio challenges Mateo.
episodes.title: El refugio del Buitre

episodes.synopsis: Isabel will try to rescue her daughter and Fernanda, but she'll need more than luck and accomplices to evade security at the hacienda.
episodes.title: La sangre llama

episodes.synopsis: Isabel is forced to tell Mateo where his grandson is. Meanwhile, Ramona advises Mateo to let others do the dirty work. Amanda misses her family.
episodes.title: Mateo va por más

episodes.synopsis: Circe knows how to attract men...and El Buitre is no exception. Claudio shows what he's made of, though he doesn't know he's missing something.
episodes.title: Provocación

episodes.synopsis: Circe receives key information to kill Diego. Mami Chula uses the same frequency as Mateo's truck. Lupe and Alberto play an important role.
episodes.title: La carnada

episodes.synopsis: In the desert, Mateo's victims are dehydrated and running out of air. A hole in the truck becomes a coveted prize. Salas gives Diego some information.
episodes.title: Asfixia

episodes.synopsis: Diego and Victoria search for Isabel, who's nowhere to be found. Only one place remains to look: the morgue. Mauricio orders Chávez to arrest Hidalgo.
episodes.title: Lágrimas de sangre

episodes.synopsis: El Buitre makes Victoria an offer to get her to hand Diego over. She and Inés are a thorn in Mateo's side. Circe goes after Ricas to find Hidalgo.
episodes.title: El monstruo quiere negociar

episodes.synopsis: Circe detains Diego and finds his weak spot: his family. Taking advantage of this, she leaves him in an abandoned warehouse, with a gun and a choice.
episodes.title: El huérfano en sus garras

episodes.synopsis: Nana, Circe, Apá and El Buitre make an unplanned pact. Mami Chula's reputation as a dangerous traitor is indisputable. Ricas and Diego mourn a loss.
episodes.title: Juntos, pero no revueltos

episodes.synopsis: El Buitre's suspicions are confirmed and Diego is involved. A confession unleashes a beating and Circe is exposed. Hidalgo has important information.
episodes.title: Traición imperdonable

episodes.synopsis: Mateo's leadership is at risk, so Mauricio launches a campaign against the huachicoleros and their leader. Enraged, El Buitre responds in cold blood.
episodes.title: El Buitre come carroña

episodes.synopsis: Mateo isn't sure how much Isabel knew about Diego. Amanda asks questions. Her grandfather vows to bring Ricas in and keep the enemy from sinking him.
episodes.title: La historia al revés

episodes.synopsis: Mateo tries to make the most of his final goodbye to Isabel. Amanda vows to find the person responsible for her mother's death.
episodes.title: El juramento de Amanda

episodes.synopsis: Victoria tells Diego he is putting custody of Ricas at risk. Diego is ready to find crucial evidence. A wedding abroad proves convenient for Mateo.
episodes.title: Batalla por la custodia

episodes.synopsis: Amanda is unafraid and determined to go after her grandfather's enemy. Everyone is looking for Ricas and believes that Corona took him by force.
episodes.title: La osadía

episodes.synopsis: Diego and Mateo come before the judge to air their grievances. Victoria tries to control her client. Mateo shines as the concerned grandfather.
episodes.title: Cara a cara en la corte

episodes.synopsis: Diego and his followers must train and procure weapons. Victoria leads Hidalgo to an impressive hidden arsenal. Joselito plays dirty with Circe.
episodes.title: Tambores de guerra

episodes.synopsis: Mateo tries to bribe Judge Sequeira to win custody of his grandchildren; the scales begin to tip in his favor. Father Rafael takes Lamas from school.
episodes.title: A cualquier precio

episodes.synopsis: Jaimito and Ignacio risk everything and go to Mateo's hacienda. Patricia and Rubén are ready to take Fernanda to the hospital, but things go awry.
episodes.title: La misión

episodes.synopsis: Salas challenges Mateo and warns him that someday he will pay for everything. Corona thinks about Fernanda. Rubén winds up as an unwilling accomplice.
episodes.title: Rumbo al más allá

episodes.synopsis: Victoria sees Diego as the man who pushes her to fight for her ideals. Someone who gives people hope. She has never met anyone like him before.
episodes.title: Impulsos del corazón

episodes.synopsis: Victoria recognizes Jaimito in one of Joselito's publications. Now that they know about the plan to rescue Fernanda, maybe they could find Salas.
episodes.title: Tras una pista de Salas

episodes.synopsis: Amanda sees Benito, and Mateo takes matters into his own hands. A lie comes to light, and suspicion of a betrayal brings serious consequences.
episodes.title: Mateo saca el látigo

episodes.synopsis: Mateo now sees how to end the war with the Arismendi family: by trading Circe for El Cachorro. Claudio vows to turn Mateo's hacienda into a graveyard.
episodes.title: Por las nalgas de Circe

episodes.synopsis: Mateo loses control. Lupe becomes nervous and Victoria offers to take Alberto far away, but he thinks of the consequences. Everyone is under threat.
episodes.title: En busca del traidor

episodes.synopsis: After Salas's statement, Diego organizes a rescue. Victoria tells him to bring Lupe and Alberto. El Buitre learns of the plan involving El Cachorro.
episodes.title: Autodefensas en acción

episodes.synopsis: If Fernanda talks, Mateo will go to jail. Chávez is ordered to find her as soon as possible. Even if Rafael wanted to help, it would be very risky.
episodes.title: Un escondite para Fernanda

episodes.synopsis: Diego does not believe the police, but he knows that Victoria trusts Bracho, so together they devise a plan that could cost them dearly.
episodes.title: La triple alianza secreta

episodes.synopsis: Victoria is worried, so Diego calls Mateo and makes a promise. Bracho starts to build the case and thinks of a trustworthy prosecutor.
episodes.title: El coraje de Diego

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda is ready to see Salas, with the help of Father Rafael and a strategy that seeks to mislead everyone. Chávez takes statements at the hospital.
episodes.title: Encubierta

episodes.synopsis: Diego and Ricas want to see Amanda and file an injunction against Mateo. Corona bans her from seeing her stepfather and brother. No one will concede.
episodes.title: Directo al matadero

episodes.synopsis: Mateo discovers Diego's self-defense group and attacks, convinced that striking first gives him an advantage. Frida is the bait for Hidalgo's gang.
episodes.title: El siguiente golpe

episodes.synopsis: Victoria gathers enough information to blackmail The Man and gets the coordinates to bring back Nuria and Frida. Diego tries to intervene.
episodes.title: Doble rescate

episodes.synopsis: The judge has made a decision on custody of the Corona siblings. Victoria, Diego and Fuentes await a verdict that will mark a before and after.
episodes.title: La sentencia

episodes.synopsis: Diego convinces Ricas there's only one way to stop Mateo from taking him. As Victoria says goodbye, she receives an unexpected message from Alberto.
episodes.title: La huida

episodes.synopsis: Several things surprise Ricas on arriving at Mateo's hacienda. Amanda sheds tears of regret, makes a call from the heart, and fearfully asks for help.
episodes.title: Perdón

episodes.synopsis: Mateo's men surprise Diego and Apá. War with the Arismendi family looms; Corona already has a strategy. Victoria enlists a doctor as an accomplice.
episodes.title: Rodeados

episodes.synopsis: Victoria cannot believe that Diego would consider allying with El Apá. During a heated argument, she gives him a warning. Then everything changes.
episodes.title: No a la traición

episodes.synopsis: Mateo threatens Father Rafael, asking Mauricio to expel him from the country since he is a hindrance. The search for Salas and Bracho intensifies.
episodes.title: Pecador

episodes.synopsis: In a desperate attempt to reach the hideout where Bracho took Salas, Diego and Deivid confront a patrol car and become involved in a shootout.
episodes.title: Sin rastro de Salas

episodes.synopsis: Tired of being in hiding, Fernanda ignores Diego's advice and goes to the hospital to see Salas. Mateo finds out and sets a life or death ultimatum.
episodes.title: 72 horas

episodes.synopsis: Chucho and Diego have a man-to-man discussion. Hidalgo realizes that money can undermine loyalty. Fernanda is very worried.
episodes.title: Lavado de cerebro

episodes.synopsis: Diego goes to "turn himself in" to El Buitre while Circe attends to business matters with Nana and Jaimito, unaware that someone is stalking them.
episodes.title: Ya se armó

episodes.synopsis: Diego confirms to Deivid that he is allied with El Buitre, but doesn't tell Victoria. He knows joining the Arismendis could ruin their relationship.
episodes.title: Noticia bomba

episodes.synopsis: Now, El Apá's life is worth three, as the exchange includes Circe, Diego, and the counterfeiter Jaimito. Mateo's enemies devise a rescue plan.
episodes.title: Tres por uno

episodes.synopsis: Both sides will give their all on a decisive night. Victoria puts into action a bold new strategy to attack Mateo's criminal network from the inside.
episodes.title: Es hora

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda manipulates the situation to protect Diego and he is completely bewildered. Hidalgo looks for Victoria, but doesn't find her.
episodes.title: Las maniobras de Fernanda

episodes.synopsis: Humberto gives Jaime a photo of Valentina Acosta, a supposed friend of Victoria's, so that he can falsify her identity. Diego is suspicious.
episodes.title: Irreconocible

episodes.synopsis: The Man must make good on the deal and help Victoria. Mateo will oversee that group of immigrants, so there's more risk, but she goes through with it.
episodes.title: Como liebre en el bosque

episodes.synopsis: The Man does his job and Victoria is left alone, not knowing what will become of her. Diego confesses to Father Rafael, who tells him about Victoria.
episodes.title: Sobre los mismos pasos

episodes.synopsis: Chávez launches an operation and El Buitre abandons a funeral in full swing. A chase ensues and Circe tries to vanish into the cemetery.
episodes.title: Los demonios andan sueltos

episodes.synopsis: Now that Victoria is on the inside of organized crime, The Man drugs her to entrap her in prostitution. Diego confronts Humberto about Lamas.
episodes.title: En carne propia

episodes.synopsis: The police go to the bar where Mateo runs his business. Victoria could testify, but she can't talk. El Míster bribes the authorities to drop the case.
episodes.title: Negocio en picada

episodes.synopsis: Diego hears a name and takes the risk of looking for information about Victoria. Meanwhile, Mateo strives to find out who she is and what she wants.
episodes.title: Tratos con la mafia

episodes.synopsis: Victoria confronts her kidnapper, warning him not to kill her. Seeking evidence against Mateo, she confides in Nuria, who tells El Míster the truth.
episodes.title: Agallas

episodes.synopsis: Hearing gunshots on a call, Diego urges Humberto to tell him where Victoria is. Disguised as Valentina, the lawyer discovers hell in the maquilas.
episodes.title: Se encienden las alarmas

episodes.synopsis: On Victoria's trail, Diego and Deivid arrive at a bar. No one recognizes her, but one of the girls mentions that there's a brave lawyer among them.
episodes.title: La ruta hacia Victoria

episodes.synopsis: Mateo proposes a pact and summons El Buitre alone, in secret, and unarmed. Diego senses something is off. Victoria recognizes him and tells Nuria.
episodes.title: Mateo en ebullición

episodes.synopsis: Victoria's mission becomes more difficult when she suspects that Diego is part of the plan. She takes measures after talking to her accomplice.
episodes.title: Más cerca que nunca

episodes.synopsis: Help capturing Mateo isn't enough. Handing him over to the authorities is no guarantee he'll be locked up for life, so Diego proposes an alternative.
episodes.title: Van por el verdugo

episodes.synopsis: Fixated on her goal, Victoria informs the authorities she's no longer alone. Diego vows to rescue her, sending her a message through Nuria.
episodes.title: El dato

episodes.synopsis: El Míster fears for the safety of his children, so Victoria offers him a way to protect them. A secret meeting exceeds the limits of the mission.
episodes.title: El informante

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda implements her plan and distracts Mateo with her charms. Alberto, Ricas and Amanda escape, but the border crossing is too busy.
episodes.title: Todo por la familia

episodes.synopsis: A risky escape attempt puts Fernanda in danger. Victoria and Nuria rely on The Man to steal more evidence that compromises Mateo.
episodes.title: Jugadas peligrosas

episodes.synopsis: On Mateo's orders, Darwin threatens Victoria and El Míster at gunpoint. Diego, the federal agent, and team go after them. Ramona makes an accusation.
episodes.title: El rescate

episodes.synopsis: A dossier with ironclad evidence doesn't seem to be enough to arrest Corona. A biased judge and government involvement lead Diego to confront Mateo.
episodes.title: La justicia en sus manos

episodes.synopsis: Circe learns that Vidal is in jail and decides to take his money; going after Ramona, she has an unexpected reunion. El Buitre gets even with Jaimito.
episodes.title: El enemigo en común

episodes.synopsis: Victoria believes they only have what Chucho was able to get out of Vidal in prison, but there is overwhelming evidence.
episodes.title: Broche de oro
